Use FireFox SQLite Manager to create, query, and view database. 
Code connects to database, queries on it, and closes. 

Add jars to project path (in Resources folder).
can be found at:
https://bitbucket.org/xerial/sqlite-jdbc/downloads

Syntax for connecting to db:
Connection con = DriverManager.getConnection("jdbc:sqlite:DBPath...");

Syntax for SQL insert queries:

INSERT INTO RECIPE (Name,Description,Ingredients,Instructions) VALUES (?,?,?,?);


		